    "remarks_html": "<p>Reports success or failure on a password change operation.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Status</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x00</code></td>\n<td>Change accepted, requires proof</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x01</code></td>\n<td>Account doesn't exist</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x05</code></td>\n<td>Account requires upgrade; see <a href=\"/packet/200/sid-auth-accountupgrade\">C&gt;S 0x57 SID_AUTH_ACCOUNTUPGRADE</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other</td>\n<td>Unknown (failure)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>If an error occurs, the salt and server key values are set to zero.</p>",
